flowchart LR
    A[Start angular sweep] --> B[Rotate left/right<br/>using gyroscope]

    B --> C[Measure distance<br/>with ultrasonic sensor]

    C --> D{Distance < threshold?}

    D -->|Yes| E[Record gyro angle]
    D -->|No| B

    E --> B

    B --> F[Compute angular span]
    F --> G[Compute average angle]

    G --> H{Width within bounds?}

    H -->|Yes| I[Classify as ore]
    H -->|No| J[Classify as obstacle]
